 = \\int_{a}^{b} \\int_{g_1(x)}^{g_2(x)} f(x, y) dy dx $$</p>"},{"location":"yunchou/teach/#_3","title":"\u6982\u7387\u8bba\u516c\u5f0f","text":"<p>\u6b63\u6001\u5206\u5e03\u6982\u7387\u5bc6\u5ea6\u51fd\u6570\uff1a</p> <p>$$  f(x) = \\frac{1}{\\sigma \\sqrt{2\\pi}} e^{-\\frac{(x - \\mu)^2}{2\\sigma^2}} $$</p>"},{"location":"yunchou/teach/#_4","title":"\u77e9\u9635\u8fd0\u7b97","text":"<p>\u77e9\u9635\u4e58\u6cd5\uff1a</p> <p>$$  C = A \\times B \\quad \\text{\u5176\u4e2d} \\quad C_{ij} = \\sum_{k=1}^{n} A_{ik} B_{kj} $$</p> <p>\u7279\u5f81\u503c\u95ee\u9898\uff1a</p> <p>$$  A v = \\lambda v $$</p>"}]}